Dialogue: 100,0:00:00.45,0:00:01.93,Dialogue,knights,0,0,0,,Apărați castelul!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.73,0:01:13.93,Dialogue,knight 1,0,0,0,,Încă nu a reușit să scape prințul moștenitor?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.93,0:01:17.05,Dialogue,knight 2,0,0,0,,Nu e atât de simplu! Prinții sunt prea mici ca să poată fugi repede!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.82,0:01:22.56,Dialogue,Yoel,0,0,0,,Oricum ar fi, vom apăra acest loc până la moarte!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:22.56,0:01:24.39,Dialogue,Yoel,0,0,0,,Rezistați până auziți copotul de semnal!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:42.64,0:01:45.76,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uitați omul care a provocat acest război,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:47.65,0:01:49.82,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Împăratul Imperiului Galkhein:
Dialogue: 100,0:01:50.29,0:01:52.04,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Arnold Hein.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.39,0:02:07.28,Dialogue,Yoel,0,0,0,,Să mergem!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:07.28,0:02:08.29,Dialogue,knights,0,0,0,,Am înțeles!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.40,0:03:40.70,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mi-am trăit viața la maxim.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.07,0:03:46.32,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dar...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:47.29,0:03:51.00,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Data viitoare... Data viitoare, voi...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.03,0:04:18.50,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Rishe Irmgard Weitzner!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.50,0:04:22.39,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Ești o femeie perfidă, care nu merită să fie logodnica unui prințul moștenitor!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.39,0:04:26.71,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Astăzi, chiar în acest moment, îmi anulez logodna cu tine!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:28.80,0:04:30.66,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Foarte bine. Am înțeles.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.66,0:04:31.72,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Poftim?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.78,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Stai puțin. Tocmai am spus că anulez logodna noastră.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.78,0:04:36.67,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Sigur ești îngrijorată de ce se va întâmpla cu tine acum.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.14,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Nu, chiar deloc.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.42,0:04:39.57,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.08,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Te rog să mă scuzi acum.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.08,0:04:43.73,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Ce? S-Stai!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:43.73,0:04:45.68,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Rishe? Unde te duci?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.39,Dialogue,Dietrich; background,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ascultă-mă!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.44,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Se pare că m-am întors din nou.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:47.39,0:04:51.15,Dialogue,Dietrich; background,0,0,0,,{\an8}I spent a whole week thinking about \Nhow I'd read off your list of crimes!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:51.15,0:04:54.42,Dialogue,Dietrich; background,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ascultă-mă! Hei! Hei! Vino înapoi!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:53.29,0:04:56.19,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Știu deja cum voi fi tratată.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.42,0:04:58.31,Dialogue,Dietrich; background,0,0,0,,{\an8}Stai! Rishe! Ascultă-mă când vorbesc cu tine!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:57.35,0:04:58.53,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}La urma urmei,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.82,0:05:03.47,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}asta e a șaptea oară când îmi retrăiesc viața.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.69,0:05:15.35,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chiar și acum, îmi pot aminti clar ca lumina zilei...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.35,0:05:17.66,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Prima mea viață.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:18.15,0:05:20.75,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Rishe Irmgard Weitzner!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:20.75,0:05:24.48,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Ești o femeie perfidă, care nu merită să fie logodnica unui prințul moștenitor!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:24.48,0:05:28.64,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,{\an8}Astăzi, chiar în acest moment, îmi anulez logodna cu tine!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.64,0:05:31.64,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\an8}C-Ce? Ne anulezi logodna?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.64,0:05:33.76,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Dar... de ce?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:33.76,0:05:36.14,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Vei fi exilată din acest regat.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.49,0:05:38.31,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Prințule moștenitor Dietrich...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:38.31,0:05:40.40,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Chiar vorbești serios?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:40.40,0:05:43.35,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Îți voi spune crimele de care ești vinovată.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.35,0:05:44.77,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Crime?!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.29,0:05:49.91,Dialogue,Rishe's dad,0,0,0,,Suntem o casă ducală, care are un jurământ de loialitate față de familia regală.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.91,0:05:53.04,Dialogue,Rishe's dad,0,0,0,,Când mă gândesc că tu, singura mea fiică, ai încălcat acel jurământ.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.54,Dialogue,Rishe's mom,0,0,0,,Ar trebui să-ți fie rușine, Rishe.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.54,0:05:58.42,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Sunt acuzații false! \NAscultați-mă, vă rog!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.93,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Tată! Mamă!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:03.26,0:06:05.13,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Logodna mea a fost anulată.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.94,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Familia mea m-a abandonat.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.42,0:06:10.69,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}With nothing but the clothes on \Nmy back, I wandered aimlessly.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.79,0:06:24.15,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ce mă voi face acum?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:28.05,0:06:30.47,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,E distractiv să te holbezi la pământ,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.47,0:06:31.70,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,domnișoară?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.53,0:06:34.20,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's when it happened.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.20,0:06:37.09,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's when I met that band \Nof traveling merchants.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:38.32,0:06:40.86,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,You look like you're going \Nthrough a rough patch.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:40.86,0:06:43.71,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,This cart is headed to the next \Ncountry over. Want a ride?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.71,0:06:45.53,Dialogue,Chester,0,0,0,,Ești în legătură cu asta, șefule?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:45.53,0:06:48.62,Dialogue,Chester,0,0,0,,You're a real pushover when it \Ncomes to beauties like her.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.54,0:06:52.19,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aceste persoane sunt negustori?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.27,0:06:52.19,Dialogue,traders; background,0,0,0,,{\an8}E adevărat!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.77,0:06:56.35,Dialogue,Tully; background,0,0,0,,Idiots. I've got a better eye \Nfor people than you think.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:59.05,0:07:03.05,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,Even in the moonlight, that silk \Nshines with an impressive luster.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.48,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,It's Vishkulha made, isn't it?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:06.90,0:07:11.23,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,So you're from the royal family, \Nor maybe a duke's house.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.23,0:07:13.26,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,A noble young lady like you \Nout this late can only—
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.37,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.52,0:07:18.45,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Would you buy this ring from me?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:26.52,0:07:29.59,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,We don't just buy and sell things.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:30.20,0:07:34.26,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,We find goods that set our \Nhearts ablaze—that fire us up—
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.26,0:07:37.26,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,and we sell them to people who are \Njust as excited about them as us.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.26,0:07:42.54,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,Both buyer and seller love the wares, and \Nthat's what creates the profit in the trade.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:43.58,0:07:47.02,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,That's our creed—the creed \Nof the Aria Trading Company.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.40,0:07:52.55,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,That face... You just thought, \N"that sounds like fun," didn't you?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.55,0:07:54.19,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.19,0:07:57.79,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,Your life's a blank slate right now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.54,0:08:02.08,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,Why don't you take this opportunity \Nto embark on the path of a merchant?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:02.37,0:08:06.54,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Me? I've never even considered it.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:06.54,0:08:10.97,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,You've been freed from your stifling destiny \Nas the wife of a crown prince.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:11.45,0:08:14.39,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,You can go anywhere.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.86,0:08:16.55,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,You're free to do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.17,0:08:23.22,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Free... to do what I want...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.96,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,You have a good eye.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.96,0:08:28.07,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.39,0:08:34.07,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,You possess the kind of amazing luck that \Nled you to a friendly caravan like ours!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.07,0:08:38.08,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,If you became a merchant, I think \Nthings would get pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.18,0:08:42.60,Dialogue,Tully,0,0,0,,How about it? Are you in?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.60,0:08:46.08,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Yes, please! Please teach me \Nhow to be a merchant!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:47.48,0:08:49.17,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}My first life.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.72,0:08:53.10,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}I learned how to trade under Chief Tully.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:53.62,0:08:56.69,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I set out on my own as a merchant.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.69,0:09:01.37,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}I traveled the world, pursuing my newfound \Ndream of visiting every country in it.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:02.11,0:09:04.82,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then, with just one \Ncountry left on my list,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:04.82,0:09:07.45,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was swept up in a war...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:07.84,0:09:10.50,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}and ended up losing my life.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.41,0:09:33.51,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.61,0:09:35.20,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Rishe Irmgard Weitzner!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.20,0:09:38.96,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,You are a devious woman unworthy of \Nbeing the fiancée of a crown prince!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:38.96,0:09:43.06,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Today, as of this moment, \NI annul my engagement to you!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:43.31,0:09:46.00,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Crown Prince Dietrich?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:47.99,0:09:49.61,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is all this?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:50.45,0:09:53.22,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dress and ring are just \Nas they were on that day.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:53.89,0:09:56.57,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this... a dream?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:56.69,0:09:59.82,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,You will be exiled from this kingdom.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.56,0:10:03.83,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.58,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Does the dissolution of our engagement \Nsadden you that much?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.58,0:10:08.97,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}If this isn't a dream...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.68,Dialogue,Dietrich; background,0,0,0,,{\an8}I see. I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.97,0:10:10.83,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}then I don't have a moment to lose!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:10.83,0:10:13.59,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Soon, they'll lock me out of the mansion!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.14,0:10:15.29,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,If you'll pardon me.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.29,0:10:16.84,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Huh? W-Wait!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:16.84,0:10:18.47,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Rishe? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:18.47,0:10:19.71,Dialogue,Dietrich; background,0,0,0,,{\an8}Listen to me!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.20,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you, gods!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.71,0:10:23.50,Dialogue,Dietrich; background,0,0,0,,{\an8}I spent a whole week thinking about \Nhow I'd read off your list of crimes!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.20,0:10:24.95,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't understand how, \Nbut I've been given a second chance at life!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:23.50,0:10:25.60,Dialogue,Dietrich; background,0,0,0,,{\an8}Listen! Hey! You! Come back here!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.60,0:10:28.14,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only regret I harbored about that night...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.14,0:10:31.11,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}was that I wasn't able to bring \Nmore of my personal effects with me.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:31.11,0:10:33.07,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I'd had more seed money as a merchant,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.56,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}I would have been able to grow \Nmy enterprise more quickly.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:36.59,0:10:40.95,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I just need to meet Chief Tully and \Neveryone from the Aria Trading Company again!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.48,0:10:47.25,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}But by the time I arrived, the Company's \Ncarts had already passed through.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:47.83,0:10:52.00,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can't be. Is this because I went \Nback home and gathered my things?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:58.21,0:11:01.99,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Pictorial Herbal of Foreign Medicinal \NPlants{\i0} my grandmother left me...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:03.01,0:11:05.63,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike last time, I have money.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.63,0:11:08.53,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}In which case, I just need to \Ndecide what to do with it.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:10.29,0:11:14.59,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}In my second life, I sold my possessions, \Nused the proceeds to cross the sea,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.80,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}and chose to study medicine.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:17.56,0:11:20.35,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}With information on where \Nmedicinal plants grew,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:20.35,0:11:22.70,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the knowledge of when \Nepidemics would spread,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:22.70,0:11:27.20,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was able to put the experience \NI'd gained from my first life to good use.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:28.27,0:11:30.75,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, I traveled to a kingdom in the north
Dialogue: 100,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.41,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}and saved a sickly prince.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:34.04,0:11:37.00,Dialogue,Michel,0,0,0,,Your complexion is looking much better, Kyle.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:37.47,0:11:39.30,Dialogue,Kyle,0,0,0,,Thank you, Weitzner.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:39.30,0:11:42.51,Dialogue,Kyle,0,0,0,,I feel so well today that \NI even surprise myself.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:42.51,0:11:44.51,Dialogue,Kyle,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to your medicine.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:44.71,0:11:46.26,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:46.26,0:11:50.79,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}My life as an herbalist was fulfilling \Nand incredibly rewarding.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:51.32,0:11:55.02,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}But once again in my second life, \Njust as I'd been in my first...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:55.02,0:11:58.35,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was swept up in a war and died.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:07.69,0:12:10.29,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Rishe Irmgard Weitzner!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:10.29,0:12:14.13,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,You are a devious woman unworthy of \Nbeing the fiancée of a crown prince!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:14.13,0:12:17.59,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Today, as of this moment, \NI annul my engagement to—
Dialogue: 100,0:12:17.59,0:12:18.84,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,I understand and comply.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.24,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Understand what?!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:20.99,0:12:23.80,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}For my third life, I set my \Nsights on something else:
Dialogue: 100,0:12:23.80,0:12:28.04,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}a specialized branch of study that \NI'd learned of in my previous life,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:28.83,0:12:31.75,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}and a genius scholar who specialized in it.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:32.31,0:12:36.88,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}For me, his was the familiar face of \Nan acquaintance from my second life,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:36.88,0:12:38.76,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doctor Michel Evan.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:39.91,0:12:42.44,Dialogue,Michel,0,0,0,,No matter how perfect you \Nbelieve your theory to be,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:42.44,0:12:47.36,Dialogue,Michel,0,0,0,,it is only through repeated experimentation \Nthat you may draw a valid conclusion.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:47.36,0:12:48.83,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Yes, Doctor!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:48.83,0:12:52.15,Dialogue,Michel,0,0,0,,You really do seem to enjoy your research.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:52.15,0:12:55.33,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Learning new things is so very exciting!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.17,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,It expands my horizons,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:57.17,0:13:00.21,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,and causes me to view even yesterday's \Nsights in a whole new light!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:01.95,0:13:04.08,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that, the good doctor and I parted ways,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:04.08,0:13:08.10,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}and as I continued my research alone, \Nonce again...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:08.47,0:13:11.39,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was swept up in a war and died.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:12.87,0:13:16.98,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}From serving as a handmaid in a \Nduke's household in my fourth life,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:16.98,0:13:20.41,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}to disguising myself as a man \Nand fighting as a knight in my sixth life...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:20.99,0:13:23.54,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}In each life, I found a sense of fulfillment,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:23.54,0:13:25.21,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I enjoyed them all very much.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:25.87,0:13:26.81,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:29.43,0:13:32.05,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}In each new life of mine, \Nonce five years have passed,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:32.05,0:13:34.38,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}I die without fail.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:35.25,0:13:38.33,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even when I didn't die from \Nbeing swept up in the war,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:38.33,0:13:41.18,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}I spent my days so busy \NI nearly died from overwork!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:41.63,0:13:44.34,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now, I find myself reliving \Nmy life for the seventh time.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:44.65,0:13:48.34,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to spend this go-around taking it easy.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:48.34,0:13:50.13,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}And more than anything else,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:50.91,0:13:53.75,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}I swear I'll live a long life this time!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:54.82,0:13:56.27,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.90,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}up until this point, I've always \Nleft through the main entrance.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:01.55,0:14:05.07,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}But as I am now, this way will be quicker—
Dialogue: 100,0:14:09.76,0:14:13.19,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,I'm so very... sorry...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:21.68,0:14:23.55,Dialogue,Arnold,0,0,0,,You certainly charged around that corner—
Dialogue: 100,0:14:26.46,0:14:28.57,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Emperor Arnold Hein!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.59,Dialogue,Arnold,0,0,0,,You know who I am?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:31.05,0:14:33.68,Dialogue,Arnold,0,0,0,,This is the first time \NI've come to this kingdom.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:36.04,0:14:40.17,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,My name is Rishe Imgard Weitzner.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:40.93,0:14:43.33,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Though this is the first time we have met,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:43.33,0:14:45.69,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,I must say that your reputation precedes you.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:45.69,0:14:48.95,Dialogue,Arnold,0,0,0,,Just now, you called me \N"emperor," didn't you?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:50.56,0:14:55.41,Dialogue,Arnold,0,0,0,,As my father, the emperor, still lives, \NI am no more than a crown prince. And yet...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.69,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:00.39,0:15:03.24,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,My deepest apologies, Your Royal Highness.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:03.65,0:15:08.05,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,In my flustered state, it seems \NI misspoke most disrespectfully.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:08.51,0:15:12.28,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,However, my engagement has presently \Nbeen annulled, so I am in no small hurry.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:12.28,0:15:14.02,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,I must take my leave now.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:16.61,0:15:18.02,Dialogue,Arnold,0,0,0,,A broken engagement?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.15,Dialogue,Arnold,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:01.42,0:16:02.47,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:12.42,0:16:14.20,Dialogue,Oliver,0,0,0,,Has something happened?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:14.36,0:16:16.90,Dialogue,Arnold,0,0,0,,Oliver, ready my horse.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:16.90,0:16:18.42,Dialogue,Oliver,0,0,0,,As you command.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:18.42,0:16:20.20,Dialogue,Oliver,0,0,0,,What are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:33.72,0:16:36.85,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,This body has far too little endurance.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:36.85,0:16:39.06,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,I'll have to train all over again.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:40.84,0:16:41.77,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:44.48,0:16:46.73,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,I've spent a week planning it—my masterpiece!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:47.04,0:16:49.27,Dialogue,Ermitte knight,0,0,0,,Prince Dietrich! It's Lady Rishe!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.23,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.99,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Out of the way! You, let me pass!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:53.21,0:16:54.89,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,You took your time, Rishe.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:54.89,0:16:56.99,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,You don't wish to hear your beloved,
Dialogue: 100,0:16:56.99,0:17:00.25,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,me, speak more words of \Ncondemnation. I understand.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:00.25,0:17:02.40,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,However, it won't go as you wish.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:02.40,0:17:05.34,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Bringing the hammer of justice down \Nupon wicked women such as you
Dialogue: 100,0:17:05.34,0:17:08.25,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,is one of my duties as the \Nfuture king of this land!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:06.45,0:17:08.25,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\an8}Not only did I fail to make it in time,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:08.25,0:17:11.51,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,this is the absolute worst \Ntiming of any of my lives.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:11.51,0:17:13.78,Dialogue,Rishe; background,0,0,0,,If only I'd arrived later \Nthan in my first life,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:13.78,0:17:16.43,Dialogue,Rishe; background,0,0,0,,I might have avoided seeing his face again.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.43,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,{\an8}What are you mumbling about?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:17.33,0:17:18.54,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,It's just as I thought.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:19.26,0:17:21.77,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,At the soirée, you reacted \Nindifferently to my proclamation,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:21.77,0:17:24.57,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,but it seems to me that you \Nare deeply saddened at heart.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:24.57,0:17:25.27,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:25.27,0:17:29.79,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,My annulment of the engagement has you in \Nsuch despair that you don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:29.79,0:17:32.53,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,You've been walking, wandering, heartbroken.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:32.53,0:17:35.15,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,I can tell that much with a single glance!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:35.15,0:17:38.66,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Your dress is covered in mud, \Nand you have wounds all over your body.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.79,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,To think that the grief of an engagement \Nbroken reduced you to such a state—
Dialogue: 100,0:17:41.79,0:17:43.29,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:43.29,0:17:44.07,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:44.07,0:17:46.37,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Grief does not dirty a dress.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:46.37,0:17:50.71,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,More importantly, I am not sad that \Nyou have broken our engagement.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:50.71,0:17:52.25,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:52.63,0:17:56.13,Dialogue,woman 1,0,0,0,,Has the crown prince been \Nspurned by Lady Rishe?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:56.13,0:18:00.20,Dialogue,man,0,0,0,,But Lady Rishe wasn't the one \Nwho broke the engagement, was she?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:00.20,0:18:04.28,Dialogue,woman 1,0,0,0,,Still, the crown prince looks \Nmore hurt than she does to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:05.04,0:18:06.39,Dialogue,man,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:06.39,0:18:08.35,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,You there! You're being disrespectful!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:08.35,0:18:09.40,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,The nerve of you peasants!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:09.40,0:18:14.35,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am truly glad I did not have to spend \Nany of my lives married to this person.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:15.05,0:18:19.64,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Your Royal Highness, you are meant \Nto protect and cherish your people.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.96,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,You mustn't speak like you just did.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:21.96,0:18:24.31,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,You are the one who needs \Nto correct their demeanor.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:24.31,0:18:26.80,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Don't you have any intention \Nof asking for my forgiveness?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:26.80,0:18:28.18,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,No. Not the slightest.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:28.18,0:18:31.66,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,In fact, I'm filled with gratitude \Nto you for breaking our engagement.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:31.66,0:18:32.67,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:33.43,0:18:36.01,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Don't laugh at me!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:36.01,0:18:39.01,Dialogue,Marie,0,0,0,,That's right! You're so mean, Lady Rishe!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:39.01,0:18:44.06,Dialogue,Marie,0,0,0,,Please, don't hurt my precious Prince \NDietrich any more than you already have!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:44.06,0:18:45.52,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Lady Marie?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:45.52,0:18:49.81,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Rishe, you bullied my darling \NMarie and made her cry, didn't you?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:49.81,0:18:51.40,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,I've heard all about it!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:51.40,0:18:56.65,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Did you think that a woman as \Ntwisted as you could become queen?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:58.69,0:19:01.16,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Please, rest at ease.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:01.45,0:19:04.51,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,I will obey your decree regarding \Nour broken engagement.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:04.95,0:19:09.32,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,I will never again show \Nmyself before either of you.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:09.32,0:19:10.17,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:11.19,0:19:15.40,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Ever since I was a child, I believed that \Nmy position as fiancée to the crown prince
Dialogue: 100,0:19:15.40,0:19:17.53,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,was all that gave my life worth.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:18.21,0:19:19.93,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,But I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:20.27,0:19:22.99,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,I can find my worth myself.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:22.99,0:19:25.43,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Now that I know that, I have all I need.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:25.43,0:19:28.02,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:31.07,0:19:34.71,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,I do not require your presence in my life.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.37,Dialogue,Marie,0,0,0,,Prince Dietrich!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:39.88,0:19:41.91,Dialogue,Marie,0,0,0,,You're so mean, Lady Rishe!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:41.91,0:19:43.10,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Lady Marie.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:43.65,0:19:48.30,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Whatever lies you may tell to frame me, \NI hold no anger toward you.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:49.27,0:19:52.54,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Your marriage to His Royal Highness \Nis for your family's sake, isn't it?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:52.54,0:19:54.60,Dialogue,Marie,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:55.22,0:19:57.29,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,But please don't forget.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:57.29,0:20:01.22,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,If your future isn't one you wish for yourself, \Nthen there isn't any point to it.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:01.50,0:20:04.36,Dialogue,Marie,0,0,0,,One I wish for?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:04.89,0:20:09.50,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Finding happiness for your family, \Nand finding happiness for yourself...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.23,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,You should be able to do both at once.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:11.66,0:20:16.86,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Please lead a life where both you \Nand your family can keep smiling.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:21.63,0:20:24.60,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Now, the nuisance will remove herself.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.49,Dialogue,Marie,0,0,0,,Lady Rishe!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:26.49,0:20:30.37,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I have is the clothes on my back, \Njust as I did in my first life.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:27.13,0:20:28.44,Dialogue,Dietrich; background,0,0,0,,{\an8}Stop, Rishe!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:28.44,0:20:30.88,Dialogue,Dietrich; background,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, knights! Apprehend Rishe!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:30.37,0:20:33.00,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, where shall I go from here?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:30.88,0:20:31.89,Dialogue,knights,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sir!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:33.00,0:20:37.09,Dialogue,knight 1,0,0,0,,Um, Lady Rishe? If you could \Nwait for just a moment...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:47.60,0:20:49.95,Dialogue,Arnold,0,0,0,,As I thought. It seems you're \Nquite the sword master.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:50.59,0:20:54.08,Dialogue,Arnold,0,0,0,,Where did you learn those sword skills?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:54.08,0:20:55.90,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}Arnold Hein.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:56.95,0:20:58.36,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:58.36,0:21:01.51,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,And my skills are not so great as \Nto be deserving of praise from you.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:02.33,0:21:06.34,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,You were holding back with \Nthat strike, weren't you?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:08.16,0:21:11.41,Dialogue,Dietrich,0,0,0,,Hey, who are you? Get away from Rishe!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.43,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Everyone, remain as you are!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:13.43,0:21:17.75,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,We mustn't move aggressively against \Nthe crown prince of Galkhein.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:17.75,0:21:20.42,Dialogue,Deitrich,0,0,0,,The crown prince of Galkhein?!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:20.79,0:21:25.41,Dialogue,man 2,0,0,0,,The beast of a prince said to have single-\Nhandedly annihilated a troop of knights?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:25.41,0:21:28.18,Dialogue,woman 1,0,0,0,,Stop that! You'll be killed, too!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:28.73,0:21:32.59,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Prince Arnold, may I ask \Nwhat brings you here?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:32.59,0:21:36.26,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,I assume you didn't draw \Nyour sword just for sport.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:36.26,0:21:37.19,Dialogue,Arnold,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:38.34,0:21:41.65,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}My sixth life ended at the hands of this man.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:42.27,0:21:45.86,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, he will cause a war \Nthat will envelop the whole world.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:46.49,0:21:50.04,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,{\i1}The war that causes my death.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:57.13,0:21:57.99,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:58.84,0:22:01.59,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Ce tot faci?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:04.05,0:22:06.61,Dialogue,Arnold,0,0,0,,I apologize for my sudden discourtesy.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:07.62,0:22:09.35,Dialogue,Arnold,0,0,0,,I have something I wish to ask of you.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:09.35,0:22:10.65,Dialogue,Arnold,0,0,0,,Would you please...
Dialogue: 100,0:22:12.63,0:22:15.61,Dialogue,Arnold,0,0,0,,do me the honor of becoming my wife?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:17.31,0:22:18.34,Dialogue,Rishe,0,0,0,,Ce?
